**Shrinking World Guides**

Shrinking World Guides provide you with tips for how to thrive in the modern world.  Learn how to
apply technology to simplify your life. Discover small changes that will make things a lot easier
for you. Here you will find pointers that help you use technology to solve real-world problems.

Learn more at http://guide.shrinking-world.org

